{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b5c261439c","title":"某首长（讽刺诗）","origin":"《重庆市右派言论选辑第二集》（内部文件，只供领导同志参考，请勿外传和翻印），中共重庆市委宣传部办公室编印，1957年8月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4af93c0dc6","index":0,"year":1957,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"b5c261439c"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"3d6e05a0be","name":"重庆"},{"id":"980ae8e8e3","name":"（蒋柏龄）"},{"id":"b7da59db6e","name":"江陵"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f067baa17a","type":"title","text":"某首长（讽刺诗）","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b5c261439c"},{"id":"cae2b069a0","type":"authors","text":"重庆江陵（蒋柏龄）","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b5c261439c"},{"id":"3843eda9fa","type":"paragraph","text":"[编者按：江陵，真名蒋柏龄，男，29岁，地主出身，学生成份，现在重庆市公安局工作。解放前蒋柏龄在特务报纸“天地报”做“学生天地栏”编辑，解放后常以写作为幌子，在“艺术夸张”的美名下四处投寄谩骂、污蔑党政领导的稿件。这首诗“某首长”即是丑化、歪曲领导形象的一例。]","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b5c261439c"},{"id":"9223c29e4f","type":"paragraph","text":"有这么一位首长，","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b5c261439c"},{"id":"76cbc81a26","type":"paragraph","text":"口口声声把真理维护和宣扬；","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b5c261439c"},{"id":"5d3778a376","type":"paragraph","text":"尽管只站在大门之边，","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b5c261439c"},{"id":"4e593010e2","type":"paragraph","text":"从不入室也不升堂，","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b5c261439c"},{"id":"75ffdff4ee","type":"paragraph","text":"指手划脚喧喧嚷嚷，","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b5c261439c"},{"id":"34fccbc0b0","type":"paragraph","text":"言语乏味不痛不痒。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b5c261439c"},{"id":"2d6eae6f65","type":"paragraph","text":"然而，","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b5c261439c"},{"id":"74dfd115b9","type":